HEADWORD: Bill book
<hw>Bill" book`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <fld>(Com.)</fld> <def>A book in
which a person keeps an account of his notes, bills, bills of exchange,
etc., thus showing all that he issues and receives.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bill broker</ent>⟦br⟧
